      %h3
        Welcome back,
        = @user.full_name
      %p
        You are currently signed up to the
        = succeed "." do
          %b Free Trial Plan
        %br/
        %a{:href => "#"} Upgrade now?
    .column.width3
      %h4 Last login
      %p
        Monday July 12th, 2010 at 11:32am from 127.0.0.1
